Class GraphDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • zym.tensorflow.general.GraphDriver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class GraphDriver
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Closeable
    Read a TensorFlow Graph that is saved by graph.as_graph_def() and graph_util.convert_variables_to_constants() for making predictions. 读取用 graph.as_graph_def()和graph_util.convert_variables_to_constants()保存的TensorFlow图 用来出预测。
